               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Liturgical miscellanea
 I-1) Excerpts from Säʿatat za-lelit
                     “Horologium for the Night Hours” (fols. 5r-12v)
 I-2) Excerpt from Maṣḥafa
                     ʾaslǝṭi, Lectionary for the entire year (fols. 12v-22v)
 I-3) Excerpts from
                     Maṣḥafa qǝddase “Missal” (fols. 22r-47r)
 - Fǝtḥat za-wald “Absolution of
                     the Son” (fols. 22r-24v)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
